headline: Nvidia (NVDA) Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of leading designer of graphics chips Nvidia (NASDAQ:NVDA) jumped 6% in the afternoon session after the company said it would sell more than 18,000 of its AI chips (GB300 Blackwell chips) to Saudi Arabian company Humain to be used in a 500 megawatt data-center project. The agreement also includes further expansion with "several hundred thousand" additional chips potentially planned for delivery within five years.
